LLM_response_editer_en:
Depending on the status of the screen image, you need to click in the title area. In the image, the title area is located in the middle of the top of the screen and marked with the prompt text "Click to add Title". We will use the mouse action to click this area.```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 512, "height": 237}}
]
```In actual operation, you may need to fine tune the values of 'width' and 'height' to accurately click in the title area.
